The '''convert rail''' button will activate a drag-and-drop tool that allows you to convert one type of rail to another (rail -> monorail -> maglev). This tool can be used on [[en/Manual/Building tracks|rail]], [[en/Manual/Building depots|depots]], [[en/Manual/Stations]] and [[en/Manual/Waypoints]].


Trains you already have running should be send to the depot and then destroyed [[en/Manual/Sell entire train|completely]].

Only empty depots can be converted.